Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.67,0:00:10.99,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:19.15,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.36,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:38.64,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,After the Star Festival, the king \Nmade a very important announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.11,0:00:41.56,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,The Eye of the Midnight Sun's \Nhideout has been located.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.92,0:00:45.52,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,We are going to launch an \Nall-out attack on the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:47.02,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,To that end,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:50.82,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,I have decided to gather an even more \Nselect group from the Magic Knights
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:54.15,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,to form the ultimate hand-picked unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:58.41,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,They will be called... the Royal Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:56.53,sign_24686_306_The_Royal_Knight,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.53,0:00:56.78,sign_24686_306_The_Royal_Knight,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Ro
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:00:57.03,sign_24686_306_The_Royal_Knight,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Royal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.03,0:00:57.28,sign_24686_306_The_Royal_Knight,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Royal Kni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:00:58.41,sign_24686_306_The_Royal_Knight,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Royal Knights
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.17,0:01:01.20,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A test involving all of the Magic Knights
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.20,0:01:06.87,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,for a chance to join the Royal \NKnights was about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.25,0:01:32.02,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(187,1)}The Royal Knights Selection Test
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:42.30,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief. We finally return from \Nour expedition, and now this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:45.60,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Do anything else, and you'll \Nbe obstructing public duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:48.89,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,As a Magic Knight, \NI'll have to dispose of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:52.58,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea who this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:56.03,sign_4119_23_Vice_Captain_of_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1027,1)\blur3}Vice Captain of the Purple Orcas\N{\fs30}Xerx Lügner
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:56.03,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Vice Captain of the \NPurple Orcas, Lord Xerx Lügner!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:03:01.72,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,His power and virtue are what made \Nthe Purple Orcas who they are today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:03.20,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He's the Saint of Pure Ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:05.75,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell would I know \Nabout this pompous jackass?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:09.54,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,"The Saint of Pure Ice"? \NWhere's this ice of yours, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:13.54,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,He looks more like a zombie \Ncovered in mud to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:15.11,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:20.51,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Two-bit flunkies shouldn't be boasting \Nabout supposed glories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:24.51,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Is your great master there such \Na piece of trash that he needs you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:25.84,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,to make introductions for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:26.64,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:32.44,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Obstruction of public duties? \NMust be nice being such a bigshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:36.71,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,You can say whatever the hell you \Nwant about things you don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:39.96,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Go on. Give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:44.36,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Try to strike me down in the name of justice \Nwith this all-powerful magic of yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:48.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,great vice captain of some band of thugs\Nwho likes to throw his weight around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:50.58,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You swine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:54.83,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you insult the Magic Knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:57.86,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,I shall make you regret your very \Nexistence with my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:04:00.84,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Magic: Ice Slicer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.25,0:04:11.39,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,The Saint of Pure Ice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:13.69,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:19.86,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you lost to someone like me? \NYour title as vice captain is obviously a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:30.04,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,That Magic Knight's robe is wasted on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:35.83,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... Let's see if there's anyone \Nelse around worth humiliating even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:49.06,main,Winston,0000,0000,0000,,The Royal Knights Exam! I don't know what \Nkind of exam it is, but I'm all fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:52.89,main,Winston,0000,0000,0000,,I can finally show everyone my true powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:56.79,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I beg your pardon, \Nbut even that level of power
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:59.58,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,is enough to disturb the people around you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:02.48,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,so could you consider calming down a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.15,main,Winston,0000,0000,0000,,M-My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:12.93,sign_4119_23_Vice_Captain_of_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(948,1036)\blur3}The Golden Dawn 5th Class Intermediate Magic Knight\N{\fs30}Mimosa Vermillion
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:08.09,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's Mimosa Vermillion!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.09,0:05:11.04,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I hear she's an expert \Nat healing and support,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.84,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,but she's been learning attack \Nspells lately, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:17.54,main,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,So she's a jack of all trades? \NThat's royalty for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:21.96,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa, don't start any \Ntrouble before the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:25.82,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Pointing out the lower magic level \Nof someone who's your elder...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.32,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're as obliviously rude as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:31.97,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,And you're so serious, a worrywart, \Nand a four-eyes, Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:32.97,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Four-eye—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:40.00,sign_4119_23_Vice_Captain_of_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1030,1037)\blur3}The Golden Dawn 3rd Class Intermediate Magic Knight\N{\fs30}Klaus Lunettes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:35.22,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's Klaus Lunettes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:38.66,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He's powered up a lot in the past \Nfew months, and his steel magic
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:40.14,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,is real tough to break through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:42.69,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he's also working out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:49.22,sign_4119_23_Vice_Captain_of_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(946,914)\blur3}The Golden Dawn 5th Class Intermediate Magic Knight\N{\fs30}Yuno
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:46.56,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's... the number one rookie this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:48.71,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The Wind Spirit user Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:53.74,top,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We had a date today, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.09,0:05:55.94,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I never agreed to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:06:00.47,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Then promise you'll take me \Nout on a date tomorrow! Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:01.37,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:04.30,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! Fine! The day after tomorrow works, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:06.89,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what'll happen \Nthat far into the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:12.85,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?! \NNow I'm going to mess up your hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:17.73,sign_4119_23_Vice_Captain_of_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}The Golden Dawn 2nd Class Intermediate Magic Knight\N{\fs30}Hamon Caseus
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:17.73,top,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,Well, aren't they a delight, Alecdora?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:19.21,top,Alec,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:22.27,sign_4119_23_Vice_Captain_of_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}The Golden Dawn 4th Class Senior Magic Knight\N{\fs30}Alecdora Sandler
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:22.27,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So many other top contenders \Nthat we all know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:27.24,top,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,There's a good chance a bunch of the Golden \NDawn's members are going to pass this exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:27.90,sign_4119_23_Vice_Captain_of_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}The Golden Dawn Vice Captain\N{\fs30}Langris Vaude
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:31.72,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone seems quite on edge, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:34.75,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,They should all relax a little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:37.91,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You're far too relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:40.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Klaus, Mimosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:41.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:45.63,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,A-A-A... A-Ashta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.42,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been well, Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:49.87,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I've been working out and getting stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:50.70,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:54.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'm getting fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:57.68,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta! L-L-Let's give it our all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:01.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Heck yeah! Hey, your face is a little red.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:02.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You feelin' okay, Mimosa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:05.53,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes! I-I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:08.19,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm nervous since I haven't seen \Nhim in so, so, so, so, so, so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:10.76,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're as loud as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:14.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Heya, Yuno! Weren't the hot \Nsprings great the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:15.58,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:19.62,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hot springs? What's this \Nabout hot springs, Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:22.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I lost to you in that race up the volcano,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:24.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,but I won't lose to you today, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:27.24,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do some image training to \Nprepare for when you fail today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:28.48,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,We wouldn't want you crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:30.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:32.84,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yuno, what's this about hot springs?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be having fun, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:38.52,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:41.16,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about hot springs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.63,0:07:45.36,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,Asta! Yuno! Don't forget about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:49.44,sign_4119_23_Vice_Captain_of_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}The Crimson Lion Kings 2nd Class Intermediate Magic Knight\N{\fs30}Leopold Vermillion
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:46.61,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:49.44,top,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who's going to pass this exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:50.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:51.38,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:52.49,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:55.62,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what's this about hot springs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:58.92,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, am I ever nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:01.62,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I just have to give it all I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:05.68,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you? You've got some nerve \Nwearing a Black Bulls robe, jerk face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:07.96,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave you permission, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:11.63,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno who you are, but wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:13.47,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:17.97,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to pump myself up, \Nso I changed up my hairstyle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:22.78,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You want to change your hairstyle? \NWhat brought this on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.78,0:08:25.77,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Change of mood? Did you get dumped again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.31,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:30.50,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, of course. If you changed your \Nhairstyle every time you got dumped,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:33.79,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,you wouldn't have any hair left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:34.82,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,So mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:38.92,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,In all seriousness, \NI wanted to pump myself up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:43.68,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You got it! I've got just the thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:46.63,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, wait! S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:51.43,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,So, yeah. I wanted a fresh start,\Nso I came here with a new hairstyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:55.36,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Stop lyin'! Like that wuss \Nwould ever come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:57.30,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying, and I have seniority here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:59.14,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,"Wuss"?! That's so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:02.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on, you two! Stop being so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.58,0:09:05.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's obviously Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.28,0:09:06.14,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:09.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But I think that's a bit over the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:11.58,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it totally is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:15.92,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you changed your hairstyle \Nto pump yourself up is over the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:17.44,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, totally over the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:21.91,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you frosted \Nyour tips is way over the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:26.43,top,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if it's over the top?! \N"I'm only human!" by Finral.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:29.46,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, they're so noisy. How embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:29.46,top,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Over the top! Over the top! Over the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:34.72,sign_4119_23_Vice_Captain_of_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}The Silver Eagles 3rd Class Intermediate Magic Knight\N{\fs30}Solid Silva
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:34.72,top,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Solid...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:38.89,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You came to embarrass us again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:41.64,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:46.22,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,When you lose so miserably,\Nit tarnishes the Silva family name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:49.98,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,There's still time. Hurry up and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.78,0:09:54.06,flashback,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Her magic was refined beyond belief,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.06,0:09:55.57,flashback,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,and it had dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:10:00.10,flashback,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Your magic is so crude and unsightly, \Nit's hard to believe you're royalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:01.74,flashback,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why you must surpass her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:05.42,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:07.64,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,N-Now, if you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:11.34,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I'm not afraid anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:16.01,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to show my brothers \Nand sister that I've grown!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:18.93,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,You failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.52,0:10:23.22,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you all for gathering here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:30.69,sign_14981_170_28th_Wizard_King,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1023,1)\blur3}28th Wizard King\N{\fs28}Julius Novachrono
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:30.69,sign_14981_171_Wizard_King_s_At,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1023,1)\blur3}Wizard King's Attendant\N{\fs24}Marx Francois
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:29.06,top,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let us begin the \NRoyal Knights Selection Exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:34.52,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,I shall explain the details of the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:41.59,sign_4119_23_Vice_Captain_of_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(774,1)\blur3}The King of the Clover Kingdom\N{\fs30}Augustus Kira Clover XIII
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:38.25,top,King,0000,0000,0000,,I am royalty, and this is the Royal \NKnights Selection Exam, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:44.03,italicstop,King,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, work harder to make \Nme more popular with the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:46.66,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,The exam will consist
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:53.17,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,of a team competition: a magic \Ncrystal destruction battle tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.53,0:10:57.26,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Team competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.75,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Crystal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.75,0:11:00.26,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of rules does that have?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:03.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? We aren't going \Nhead-to-head with each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:05.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make the rules too complicated, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:08.27,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,The rules are simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:12.36,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Protect your own team's crystal, \Nwhich will be placed in your area,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:16.88,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,and destroy the other team's crystal. \NThe first team to do this wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:19.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! That {\i1}is{\i0} simple! Heck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:24.46,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,If no team is able to destroy a crystal \Nwithin the 30-minute time limit,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:28.04,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,the one that has done the most \Ndamage to its target wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:32.06,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Er... We've chosen this format because...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:34.08,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Er... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.34,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:39.13,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.01,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:42.58,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,In battles against the \NEye of the Midnight Sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:45.76,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,several squads will have to work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:48.56,italics,King,0000,0000,0000,,He took the best part!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:51.28,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,We thought this would be \Nthe best way to measure
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:54.99,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,the cooperation and strategy skills \Nyou'll need at times like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.99,0:11:57.73,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,rather than simply fighting with brute force.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:12:00.10,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:04.99,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I bet I'll get to see lots of their \Nnon-combat spells this way, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:08.38,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:13.62,main,Alec,0000,0000,0000,,Which means we'll have to team up \Nwith members of the other squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.93,0:12:16.87,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let us announce the teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:23.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.19,0:12:25.34,sign_17819_208_Mimosa_Vermillio,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Mimosa Vermillion
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.19,0:12:25.34,sign_17819_209_Asta,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(177,1)\blur3}Asta
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:25.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey! I'm on the same team as Mimosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:28.57,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm on the same team as Asta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:30.83,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy, I'm oh so happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:33.82,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,but I need to concentrate! \NI need to concentrate on the exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:36.06,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,But again, what's this about hot springs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:36.81,sign_18128_216_Asta,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Asta
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:38.32,sign_18128_215_Mimosa_Vermillio,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Mimosa Vermillion
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:38.32,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:38.32,sign_18145_218_Xerx_L__gner,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(174,1)\blur3}Xerx Lügner
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:42.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Xerx Lügner? Who the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:45.88,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my bad! I'm a little late!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:55.25,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,But I bet our great Wizard King will \Nforgive me for being a tiny bit late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:57.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:13:01.64,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Xerx Lügner. It's a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:12.55,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Xerx Lügner. It's a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:19.45,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I just happened to run into \Na little old lady in distress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:23.68,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,I helped her out, since I'm a Magic Knight,\N so I ended up a little late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:25.00,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:27.86,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Is the old lady all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.86,0:13:30.38,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! She's doing great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:33.16,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:35.83,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Step away, you cur.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:40.57,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on, now. That's not very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:42.46,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:44.91,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,That would be my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:47.74,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Xerx Lügner? But that's—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:49.51,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Wizard King?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:53.26,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to pull, you bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:55.89,main,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you act like that after arriving late?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:59.81,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King is one of \Nthe only guys Sis respects!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:02.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're \Ndoing to the Wizard King?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:05.49,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. Calm down, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:10.64,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. I guess everyone \Nrespects the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:13.95,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:19.21,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push your values on me, \Nyou worthless rabble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:22.50,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,That's definitely Xerx's robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:27.41,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he gave himself quite the \Nmakeover after that long expedition of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:29.89,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,This is no laughing matter, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:36.59,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it looks like we're on the same team,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:37.89,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,so let's get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.26,0:14:41.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:49.40,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:53.94,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,The stinkiest bug in all the \NClover Kingdom, the rainbow stinkbug.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:57.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being assaulted by \Nthe scent of the rainbow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:15:00.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you actually trying \Nto get along with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:02.08,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:05.80,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I bother getting along \Nwith an airhead with a moronic face,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:09.63,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,who's a hyperactive dumbass, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:11.48,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a noisy shrimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:14.72,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty smelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:18.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.87,0:15:22.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk with a cool-looking \Nthing wrapped around your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:24.73,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you complimenting him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:28.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you even trying at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:31.56,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like all you can do is try.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:34.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you come here to get \Nchosen as a Royal Knight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:37.24,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:40.54,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to make fun of you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:42.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:45.63,main,Winston,0000,0000,0000,,Was Vice Captain Xerx always like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:48.33,main,Adrian,0000,0000,0000,,He's not at all like the rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:50.82,main,Adrian,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he was the Saint of Pure Ice,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:55.01,main,Adrian,0000,0000,0000,,but he's been stationed in the borderlands, \Nso only a few people actually know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:15:58.56,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:16:01.16,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. It looks fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:04.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:07.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna be on the \Nsame team as this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:13.11,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now... We're all Magic Knights here,\N so let's all just get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:16.62,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Haven't you forgotten about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:20.62,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,All right, everyone. \NHave you confirmed your teams?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:24.62,sign_23512_280_C_Team_Sol_Marro,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}C Team\N{\fs24}Sol Marron   Magna Swing   Kirsch Vermillion
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.74,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck is this tiny delinquent?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:29.84,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You're just too big!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:32.67,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?! Don't make me smack \Nthose lame glasses off your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:37.23,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What?! How about I bury you in the \Nground to make you a little shorter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:39.90,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,My attribute is actually earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:42.06,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Just try and bury me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:44.64,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! Men are so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:48.65,sign_24088_288_P_Team__En_Ringa,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}P Team\N{\fs24}En Ringard   Noelle Silva   Yuno
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:53.36,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm with the noisy little \Ngirl who's always with Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.69,0:16:56.61,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Well, aren't you cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:16:59.27,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,But just so you know, Yuno belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:01.08,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare lay a finger on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.08,0:17:06.01,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on the same team as the lofty \Nguy who's Asta's childhood friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.01,0:17:09.78,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening? Don't even \Nthink about getting in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:13.55,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,If you dare hold Yuno back, \NI'll make you regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.63,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, shut up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:19.64,sign_24831_297_K_Team_Puli_Ange,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}K Team\N{\fs24}Puli Angel   Luck Voltia   Klaus Lunettes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:21.99,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,H-How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:25.43,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on the same team as the \Nself-centered Luck, the Cheery Berserker?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:26.77,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:29.32,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work together and do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:31.03,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Work together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:32.32,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:38.16,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna be great teammates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:42.16,sign_23512_280_C_Team_Sol_Marro,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}E Team\N{\fs24}Finral Roulacase   Leopold Vermillion   Hamon Caseus
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:47.58,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,He's laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:50.09,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,And so is he...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:53.21,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is this team going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:57.01,sign_23512_280_C_Team_Sol_Marro,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}O Team\N{\fs24}Dimitri Blint   Solid Silva   Alecdora Sandler
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:18:01.31,main,solidP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a fan of yours, but you do \Nhave skill, so I guess I can live with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:03.85,main,solidP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go running off to act on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:07.28,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's head over to the main stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:09.02,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Cob, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:12.27,sign_4119_23_Vice_Captain_of_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Magic Knight Who Accompanies the Wizard King\N{\fs30}Cob Portaport
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:12.27,top,Cob,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:17.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Spatial magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:21.16,main,Cob,0000,0000,0000,,Right this way! Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:34.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is the stage for the crystal \Ndestruction tournament?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:35.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:38.48,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The battlefield has a wide \Nrange of different areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:41.28,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Use them to display your \Npowers to the fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:42.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:47.10,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,And here's the tournament chart, \Nwhich we determined by lottery in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:52.37,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Battle wins and losses won't directly \Naffect whether you pass or fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:55.36,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,That said, the more you win, the more \Nyou'll be able to show your true skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:58.61,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Since you have the chance, \NI hope you all strive to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:03.70,sign_27332_327_Sandler,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sandler
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:03.70,sign_27332_328_Solid,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Solid
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:03.70,sign_27332_329_Dimitri,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Dimitri
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:03.70,sign_27332_330_En,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}En
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:03.70,sign_27332_331_Yuno,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Yuno
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:03.70,sign_27332_332_Noelle,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Noelle
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:03.70,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm facing off with Solid's \Nteam right off the bat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:08.28,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,I'll happily finish you off myself, Noelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.96,sign_27532_335_Leopold,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Leopold
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.96,sign_27532_336_Hamon,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Hamon
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.96,sign_27532_337_Finral,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Finral
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.96,sign_27532_338_Bolha,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Bolha
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.96,sign_27532_339_Kyle,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Kyle
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.96,sign_27532_340_Gaston,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Gaston
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.96,sign_27532_341_Langris,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Langris
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.96,sign_27532_342_Flagil,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Flagil
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.96,sign_27532_343_Sekke,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sekke
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.96,sign_27532_344_Gareth,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Gareth
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.96,sign_27532_345_Simon,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Simon
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.96,sign_27532_346_Medeo,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Medeo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:13.21,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,If we win the first round, \NI'll be facing off with Langris.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:13.81,sign_27650_348_Xerx,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Xerx
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:13.81,sign_27650_349_Mimosa_,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Mimosa
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:13.81,sign_27650_350_Asta,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Asta
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:13.81,sign_27650_351_Kirsch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Kirsch
