Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:15.88,sign_27668_355_Solid,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Solid
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:15.88,sign_27668_356_Dimitri,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Dimitri
