Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:15.88,sign_27668_358_Yuno,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Yuno
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:15.88,sign_27668_359_Noelle,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Noelle
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:18.24,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So we'd take on Yuno's \Nteam in the finals, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:20.76,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to win until then, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:23.89,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm gonna win this whole thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.98,0:19:27.76,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we're about to begin round one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:30.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! And we're up first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:33.15,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You may attack your opponents!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:37.90,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'm sure this goes without saying, \Nmake sure you guys don't kill anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:39.65,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Let me stand out some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:45.14,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a high-level recovery mage on \Nstandby, so fight to your hearts' content!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:51.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey! It's Owen! Clover Kingdom's \Nsuper-famous sketchy doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:56.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My arms are all better now! \NI'm sorry I worried you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:07.78,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Yoohoo! The beautiful ladies of the \NBlack Bulls came to cheer you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.78,0:20:09.06,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:10.89,sign_29001_373_I_ll_do_my_best_,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'll do my best cheering!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:14.07,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.07,0:20:17.27,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But are you sure it was okay \Nfor all of you to come at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:20.99,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The captain gave us a heartfelt send-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:25.80,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? That's our captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:27.99,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,We're actually just about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:31.38,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So Asta's team is the first round?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.38,0:20:33.71,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's definitely fitting for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:38.06,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta! You'd better show them who's boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:40.49,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La! La!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.49,0:20:41.92,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see, la!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:46.48,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I'm going to miss my \Nmeal-saving prince's heroic deeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:47.93,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:51.89,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Are both teams ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:53.69,italics,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:20:59.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting hyped!
