Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:43.84,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}What's This\N About Hot Springs!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:43.29,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,What's This About Hot Springs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.33,0:22:47.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Heya, Yuno! Weren't the hot \Nsprings great the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.84,0:22:48.88,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:52.85,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hot springs? What's this \Nabout hot springs, Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.85,0:22:54.35,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.68,0:22:59.30,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "soon"? Is it \Na secret just between you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.30,0:23:02.10,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Your own private hot springs?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.10,0:23:03.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The water's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:04.49,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.49,0:23:06.53,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,They bathe together...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.53,0:23:08.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Does it itch anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.35,0:23:10.68,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,A bit below the back of my right ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:11.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.69,0:23:12.91,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:14.91,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,They shampoo each other's hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:18.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So what did I write?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.89,0:23:19.93,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Tatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.93,0:23:21.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.10,0:23:22.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn next, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.78,0:23:25.50,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Then they draw words on \Neach other's backs!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:28.51,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Hot springs? Hot springs?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.99,0:23:34.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Is she okay? Looks like she got overheated\N just thinking about the hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.39,0:23:36.30,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,She must love hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.30,0:23:37.52,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Hot springs...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.70,0:23:42.02,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Our battle is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.02,0:23:46.96,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I, Mimosa Vermillion, will do my \Nbest not to get in anyone's way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.96,0:23:50.82,main,mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 74: \N"Flower of Resolution."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.98,0:23:54.00,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 74\N\N{\fs18} Flower of Resolution
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.82,0:23:53.74,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I will make my flower bloom.
